<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Aye, my brother speaks true. The Coerced Erudite did not carry the blade in her hands but we found it on her body while rooting through her possessions. She was kind enough to wander up to us right by the zone to the Warslik, which saved me the trouble of having to venture deeper into the dungeon to lure an opponent to us. I'm surprised how underutilized Dalnir is, but very happy at the same time. Cambron and I were in Dalnir from around 2-5am est and we were the only two people in the zone the entire time. The most I've ever seen in Dalnir is 11, and that was during peak hours. I plan on sticking in Dalnir until at *least* my 32nd or 33rd season.<BR>
<BR>
I also found a Brass Goblin Flamberge in the "L" room earlier in the evening, wielded by a Coerced Goblin.<BR>
<BR>
Mikall Ravenmoon<BR>
